#: 21337012-0-127
msgctxt "21337012-0-127"
msgid "Butter! "
"\n"
"\nCheese and sausage, milk and honey and baby's breath."
"\n"
"\nKnotted sheep's guts all filled up with blood. Lashing rain and birthing screams."
"\n"
"\nWho are you to say that frog wasn't serious? He seemed damned serious to me! Next time, I won't be so kind."
"\n"
"\n— Kennixa"
msgstr "バター！\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nチーズとソーセージ、それにミルクとハチミツとかすみ草。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n血でいっぱいの羊の内臓。激しく地を打つ雨、そして出産の悲鳴。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nあのカエルは大したことなかったなんて何様？ 大したこと大有りだったが！ 次はこんなものじゃ済まない。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n――ケニクサ"

